Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.71,0:02:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crunch his head for sure this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.88,0:02:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.88,0:02:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Join our crew, Nami! Okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we team up\Nfor our common goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Epic Showdown!\NSwordsman Zoro vs. Acrobat Cabaji!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to kick your ass,\Njust like I promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:02:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you just come waltzing\Nback here, to Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! All I want is the\Nmap and the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young'uns... Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of this. You're outsiders!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my fight! I will protect my town!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your meddling!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you attack the mayor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt this old man\Nplans to die otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were plenty of other\Nways you could've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.34,0:04:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one thing you shouldn't say!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, you flashy idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flashily fire the Buggy Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you say that?! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to blow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...won't work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me the Buggy Ball...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He bounced it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something beforehand, geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:04:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.70,0:05:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Now there's fewer enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really know how\Nto freak people out...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew something was weird from\Nthe time you fought that lion!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No human can do that! Explain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that balloon-inflatey\Nthing you just did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Gum-Gum Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking what that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, a monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you flashily try to do me in...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used his henchmen as shields!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hat guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-C-Captain Buggy! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has Devil Fruit powers too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a rubber person!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rubber person?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! See!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Devil Fruit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That explains how he\Nbounced a Buggy Ball back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the greatest insult we've\Nhad since we hoisted our flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Cabaji! I'm so\Nangry I can't even fart...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cabaji! What the hell\Ndid you do to Richie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This cat? I used it as a shield,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.19,0:06:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to keep my clothes from getting dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Richie! Say something!\NAre you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:06:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Buggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Cabaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Show them your acrobat show!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Acrobat Cabaji, Chief of Staff,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,take on Captain Buggy's anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clash swords with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an honor, Roronoa Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think I would get to slay you,\Nas a swordsman myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zoro! You should\Nreally rest! I'll handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:08:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the stab wound the\Ncaptain gave him. The fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acrobat Technique: Old Man Arsonist!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? I'm sure I\Ndidn't kick you that hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He fights dirty, going\Nafter his injury like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acrobat Technique:\NMurder at the Steam Bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acrobat technique, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just an ordinary cloud of dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? A grown man\Nmoaning is disgraceful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Now do you see\Nhow foolish it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to make an enemy\Nof the Buggy Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:09:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's crazy to fight while\Nso seriously injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's hurt so bad it's almost\Nmystifying that he's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you just\Nstanding there watching?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annoying bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is poking my wound...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that much fun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why didn't you dodge that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that enough of a handicap for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'll show you the difference\Nin level between you and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Roronoa Zoro, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can mock me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My swords aim to be\Nthe world's greatest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lose even once to anyone\Nwho calls himself a swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.86,0:10:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A strong resolve keeps you going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But never fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wounds as bad as yours will be\Nmore than enough of an excuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for losing to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.21,0:10:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I lose to someone like\Nyou with such light injuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't have much of\Na bright future ahead of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go along with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pirates can injure\Nyourselves for all I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter to me\Nwhether you guys win or lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna use this chance to swipe\Ntheir treasure and get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.31,0:10:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's team up again if\Nwe ever get the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:11:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya! Good luck with the fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.52,0:11:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taste my ultimate acrobatic move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acrobat Technique:\NThe Dance of 100 Kamikaze Tops!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those aren't normal guys,\Nthat Luffy and Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing good'll come from\Nbeing involved with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now to steal their treasure\Nand chart and get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acrobat Technique:\NA Hike in the Mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acrobat Technique:\NFireworks in the Cool Summer Breeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, he's high up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sting of the Unicycle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:12:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ground-hugging Chop-Chop Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.51,0:12:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cabaji! I'll hold Zoro\Ndown! Finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of Zoro's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Look at all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's all mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doin' with\Nour treasure, now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! He woke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By Captain Buggy's orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,anyone who gets near here is to be--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm all out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.96,0:13:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My chest suddenly started to hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Your chest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.91,0:13:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.19,0:13:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chart of the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can defeat you easily enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even without my captain's help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough... I'm tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally given up, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I must say, I'm impressed\Nyou could fight with such injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant I'm tired...\Nof your crappy-ass acrobatics!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll finish you off...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with my real sword skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oni...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Giri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cabaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, the Buggy Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,beaten by mere sneak thieves...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We ain't sneak thieves...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! I'm goin' to sleep now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I'll handle the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd expect no less from the\Nnotorious Buggy Pirates' treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hauling it is exhausting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with this much treasure--!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, I gotta get\Noff this island ASAP!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We're going to the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:16:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no simple voyage nameless\Nbums like you can handle, dimwit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you gonna do in\Nthe Grand Line, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on a sightseeing trip or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get real, you flashy idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, King of the Pirates?!\NWould that make me God, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates\Nand obtain this world's treasures!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit your dreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just bring it on already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing that straw hat of yours\Nbrings back memories of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and irritates me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Memories of that damn\Ncheeky red-haired man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red-haired?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red-haired... Does that\Nmean you know Shanks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah, but why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.44,0:16:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno! Maybe I know where\Nhe is, or maybe I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?\NAre you stupid or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not as much as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.02,0:17:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't nice enough of a guy to\Njust tell you what you wanna know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll make you tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you before that ever happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt rubber can\Nbounce back blades...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, it can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chop-Chop Rice Cracker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't move in midair, can you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, quite interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are interesting abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they leave you wide open!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna carve you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chop-Chop Quick Escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Sickle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good enough, Gum-Gum!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, you keep breaking into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What a fight...\NIt's almost like I'm dreaming...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, you see that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dumbass!\NKeep pretending to be knocked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get caught up in that, and you'd\Nnever have enough lives to survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chop-Chop Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Separate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.29,0:18:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?! Now do you see, runt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.80,0:19:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.97,0:19:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Was I not supposed to\Nscratch your face or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you damage this hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever damages this\Nhat absolutely must pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I swore to the person\Nwho gave me this straw hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that I'd gather a crew\Nand become a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought there was nothing\Nthat could faze him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think he could get this upset...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem that\Nhat has a history to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.01,0:19:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that important of a hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:19:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:20:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then protect it better!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave this hat with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come bring it back to me someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've become a great pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our promise, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.42,0:21:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is this old,\Ntattered hat a treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure refers to sparkly gold,\Nsilver, and jewels...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.07,0:21:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that display their owner's grandeur!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You call this filthy\Nstraw hat a treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the hat Shanks\Nand I swore over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning this is Shanks' hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder it seemed familiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He always wore this by my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Shanks sailed\Non the same ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, back when we\Nwere pirates-in-training.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.83,0:21:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn detestable,\Nred-haired bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.14,0:21:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shanks is a great man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.91,0:21:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, his comrade?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.74,0:22:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't compare yourself to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chop-Chop Quick Escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, I'm Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never say you and Shanks\Nare comrades ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can say whatever\NI want about Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.27,0:22:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! What happened\Nbetween you and Shanks?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.11,0:22:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! How dare you\Ntear up my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.71,0:22:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna know that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.61,0:22:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one person\NI absolutely can't forgive!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.99,0:22:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll curse him for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.46,0:22:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:23:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I had\Na vision of a treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.28,0:23:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I always searched\Nfor that miraculous place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.22,0:23:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before someone else could\Nbeat me to it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the world is going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before I can even attain my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.41,0:23:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then take me to the time\Nwhen I knew nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.49,0:24:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that my memories won't fade
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.04,0:24:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready, Buggy!\NI'm gonna kick your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.51,0:24:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.48,0:24:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay for damaging the hat\Nme and Shanks swore over!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.38,0:24:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, get going, Luffy!\NBeat him up to protect my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.92,0:24:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That doesn't sound right...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.82,0:24:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's basically the same thing!\NDon't sweat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.16,0:24:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.49,0:24:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Who is the Victor?\NDevil Fruit Power Showdown!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.56,0:24:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
